492 Quest#01_02
495 Hello,#I'm#Rona#from#Popola#Village.#I'm#a#|\gifted#painter,#as#you#can#see.#Heheh!#I#|\like#to#paint#near#the#village#entrance,#and#|\sometimes#I#meet#new#adventurers#like#you|\that#happened#to#get#lost.#I#guess#helping#out|\adventurers#has#become#something#of#a#|\hobby#for#me.
497 Quest#01_03
500 Do#you#know#the#basic#controls?#Up#Arrow#|\Key:#Jump,#Down#Arrow#Key:#Move#Down#|\(Move#between#Areas),#Left#Arrow#Key:#Move#|\to#the#Left,#Right#Arrow#Key:#Move#to#the#|\Right.#I#guess#you've#already#learned#all#|\that#already,#and...#Huh?#You#really#didn't#|\know?#Well...#Everyone's#a#rookie#at#one#|\time#or#another.
502 Quest#01_04
505 Aside#from#the#arrow#keys,#you#don't#have#to#|\use#keys#other#than#the#S#key#to#use#Weak#|\Attack#for#now.#You#should#meet#some#of#the#|\townspeople#and#help#them#out:#they'll#teach#|\you#about#other#keys#that#you#can#use#for#|\useful#skills#and#magic#spells.#|\
507 Quest#01_05
510 I've#heard#that#only#a#few#adventurers#|\managed#to#explore#all#of#Beuritania#so#far.#|\I#hope#that#you'll#join#the#ranks#of#those#|\intrepid,#experienced#explorers#someday.|\
512 Quest#01_06
515 I'll#give#you#some#herbs#that'll#be#useful#|\on#your#adventures.#The#ground#here#is#|\very#fertile#so#many#trees#and#beneficial#|\herbs#grow#in#this#area.#Some#of#us#in#|\Popola#Village#make#our#living#by#gathering#|\and#selling#these#herbs#to#other#villages.
517 Quest#01_07
520 I#think#I#told#you#everything#that#I#know.#|\You#should#go#speak#to#our#village#chief#|\so#he#can#teach#you#whatever#else#you#need#|\to#learn.#Bye#now!
522 Quest#02_01
525 Welcome#to#Popola#Village.#I#am#Gandalf,#|\chief#of#this#village.#I#guess#you're#one#of#|\the#many#adventurers#that#have#been#coming#|\here#lately.#I'm#envious#of#you#young#people#|\for#your#energy#and#insatiable#curiosity|\#about#this#vast#world.#Sadly,#I'm#too#old|\to#wander:#I'd#rather#stay#here,#chat#with#|\my#visitors,#and#offer#my#help#whenever#you#|\happen#to#come#by.
527 Quest#02_02
530 It#must#have#been#tough#coming#here.#It's#a#|\little#too#early#for#you#to#rest#since#you'll#|\be#facing#more#challenges#later#on,#but#don't#|\fret.#I'm#sure#that#you#can#handle#whatever#|\comes#your#way.#That's#the#beauty#of#youth:#|\your#tenacity#and#enthusiasm#for#life#are#|\probably#your#strongest#weapons.
532 Quest#02_03
535 I#come#looking#for#you#if#I#need#some#help.#|\You're#very#kind,#and#I#know#I#can#depend#|\on#you.#Enjoy#your#travels,#adventurer.
537 Quest#02_04
540 Awww...#This#ache#in#my#back#is#a#sure#sign#|\that#there'll#be#rain#tomorrow.#Ooog...#This#|\pain#gets#worse#every#year...
