545 So#how#do#you#like#Popola?#I've#heard#that#|\strange#monsters#have#started#to#appear#in#|\the#forest,#so#be#careful#if#you#happen#to#|\pass#that#way.#Oh,#my#back!#It#seems#to#hurt#|\worse#every#year...#Let#me#tell#you,#don't#|\waste#away#your#body#by#drinking#too#much#|\like#I#did#back#in#my#day.
